title: Saturday Night Live Season 22 Complete
description:
SNL Season 22 (1996-1997)

Saturday Night Live Returns For Its 22nd Season.

ROBERT SMIGEL'S SATURDAY TV FUNHOUSE CARTOONS ALSO MAKES A DEBUT ON THE SHOW.

FORMER SNL CAST MEMBERS:PHIL HARTMAN RETURNS TO HOST THE 2nd TIME IN A ROW.
CHRIS ROCK ALSO RETURNS TO HOST THE SHOW AND MIKE MEYERS ALSO RETURNS TO HOST THE SHOW.

SEASON 22 INCLUDES WILL FERELL AS ALEX TREBECK IN CELEBRITY JEOPARDY. FIGHTING AGAINST WITH SEAN CONNERY (DARRELL HAMMOND). PLUS MANY MORE IN THIS SEASON.

SO HERE IS SEASON 22.
